event_research.event_description: The World Equestrian Center Ocala Spring series is one of the highlights of the north Florida show season, featuring high-level hunter and jumper competition at one of the most state-of-the-art venues.

venue_research.facilities: This complex includes multiple indoor and outdoor arinas. Features multiple arinas and restaurants.

city_research.description: Ocala is widely regarded as a center for equestrian activity, with top-class facilities and state-of-the-art shows.
